    "We rather intend to set a tentative baseline with this corpus and show that this first version is adequate for testing models.",
    "We tested three frameworks based on a language-modeling objective, given that this yields better results for NER than the classic embedding approaches [60,61].",
    "In the following, we describe the algorithms, the methodology and the evaluation procedure.",
    "SequenceLabelerWe first tested SequenceLabeler [62], a neural-based sequence labeling architecture.",
    "It is a Bidirectional Long-Short Term Memory (Bi-LSTM) model with a final layer implementing Conditional Random Fields (CRF); this is similar to the framework proposed in [63,64]."
